version_description: This version is an original that using Papa Roach.
Whole Song. It's an easy acoustic version for beginners. (Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uILGQABnKsc).
These chords are based on the studio version of the song (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VSecjqcO3Jk). Listen to the song for the correct chord changes.
Pretty accurate and only version so far.
My version tabs all of the lyrics and the lyrics are correct and the tuning is also correct unlike others I have seen.
It's the acoustic / demo version from Time for Annihilation.
This version is adapted to standard tuning, easy to read because all parts are with chords, contains all lyrics.
